des:
Chef Hak's brings the finest sauces and dressings from the mind of Chef Sharone Hakman to your dining table. You can use this skill to search for your favorite dressings & sauces and learn about Chef Hak's as a brand.
Here's how you can open this skill 
"Alexa, open chef hak's". 

Once inside the skill, you can ask 
- Find me a dressing 
- Search for a salad dressing
- What's your return policy
